---
title: Pan-Seared Scallops  with Wild Rice and Kiwi Salsa
description: This tropics-inspired dish has a secret ingredient: It's sweet and brings much-needed bite to the salsa, and it goes perfectly with seafood — kiwi! Served with wild rice, corn and a touch of heat, this is the pairing you didn't know you needed.
